  "title": "PASTRY CHEF",
  "description": "<p>Daily production of cakes/bread/hot food</p>\n<p>Maintain safety, health and hygiene standards</p>\n<p>Ensure workstations are clean and tidy for food preparation</p>\n<p>Clean and maintain equipment and tools</p>\n<p>Checks production schedule to determine variety and quantity of goods to bake</p>\n<p>Keeping records and relating to deliveries, inventory and production levels</p>\n<p>Testing ingredients and finished goods to ensure that each item meets food safety and quality controls</p>\n<p>Ensure stock rotation to minimize wastage</p>\n<p>Perform any other ad hoc duties when assigned</p>\n<p>MOM LICENSE NO.:16C7994</p>\n<p>EA REG. ID: R1983060</p>",
